sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Runtime as Caikit Runtime<br/>gRPC :8085 / HTTP :8080<br/>Configurable TLS
    participant TextGen as TextGeneration<br/>(Local)
    participant TextGenTGIS as TextGenerationTGIS<br/>(Remote)
    participant TGISClient as TGISGenerationClient
    participant TGIS as TGIS Backend<br/>gRPC (configurable port)<br/>Optional mTLS
    participant PeftTuning as PeftPromptTuning
    participant EmbedMod as EmbeddingModule
    participant HFModel as HuggingFace Model<br/>(Local GPU)
    participant STModel as SentenceTransformers<br/>(Local)
    participant PyTorch as PyTorch Distributed<br/>TCP :29550

    Note over Client,PyTorch: Flow 1: Local Text Generation Inference
    Client->>Runtime: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>or gRPC TextGeneration.Run<br/>Configurable TLS
    Runtime->>TextGen: route to module (in-process)
    TextGen->>HFModel: forward pass (CausalLM/Seq2SeqLM)
    HFModel-->>TextGen: generated tokens
    TextGen-->>Runtime: GeneratedTextResult
    Runtime-->>Client: JSON/Protobuf response

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 2: Remote TGIS Text Generation (Streaming)
    Client->>Runtime: POST /api/v1/task/server-streaming-text-generation<br/>or gRPC TextGeneration.ServerStreamingRun
    Runtime->>TextGenTGIS: route to TGIS module (in-process)
    TextGenTGIS->>TGISClient: create request
    TGISClient->>TGIS: gRPC GenerateStream<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    loop Token Streaming
        TGIS-->>TGISClient: GenerateStreamResponse (token)
        TGISClient-->>TextGenTGIS: yield token
        TextGenTGIS-->>Runtime: stream token
        Runtime-->>Client: stream token
    end

    Note over Client,PyTorch: Flow 3: PEFT Prompt Tuning Training
    Client->>Runtime: Training request<br/>gRPC/HTTP
    Runtime->>PeftTuning: PeftPromptTuning.train()
    PeftTuning->>HFModel: load base model
    HFModel-->>PeftTuning: model loaded
    opt Multi-GPU Training
        PeftTuning->>PyTorch: torchrun elastic launch<br/>TCP :29550 (plaintext)
        PyTorch-->>PeftTuning: distributed training coordination
    end
    PeftTuning->>PeftTuning: PEFT prompt tuning epochs
    PeftTuning->>PeftTuning: save prompt vectors to disk
    PeftTuning-->>Runtime: trained model artifact
    Runtime-->>Client: training complete

    Note over Client,STModel: Flow 4: Embedding Inference
    Client->>Runtime: POST /api/v1/task/embedding<br/>or gRPC Embedding.Run
    Runtime->>EmbedMod: route to module (in-process)
    EmbedMod->>STModel: encode(text)<br/>Optional IPEX / torch.compile
    STModel-->>EmbedMod: embedding vectors
    EmbedMod-->>Runtime: EmbeddingResult
    Runtime-->>Client: JSON/Protobuf response
